description:
Such a beautiful word, universe. your verse younited.
If you ever feel alone, think of the meaning of this word. You are never alone, you are everything and everywhere. When you feel like a loser or a winner, depressed or in love, know that the universe is only complete because of you and all energy everywhere. Once we appreciate hate or the bad or dark, we can stop to hate love. There are a gazillion versions of you and this version is needed as well.
